@startuml workflow_execution_states
title Workflow Execution - Node State Transitions

skinparam state {
    BackgroundColor<<pending>> #FFF3E0
    BorderColor<<pending>> #E65100
    BackgroundColor<<running>> #E3F2FD
    BorderColor<<running>> #1565C0
    BackgroundColor<<succeeded>> #E8F5E9
    BorderColor<<succeeded>> #2E7D32
    BackgroundColor<<failed>> #FFEBEE
    BorderColor<<failed>> #C62828
}

[*] --> Pending : Node created
Pending --> Running : Argo starts pod
Running --> Succeeded : Pod exits 0
Running --> Failed : Pod exits != 0
Running --> Error : System error

Succeeded --> [*]
Failed --> [*]
Error --> [*]

note right of Pending
  **Visual:**
  Amber/Yellow badge
end note

note right of Running
  **Visual:**
  Blue badge + animation
end note

note right of Succeeded
  **Visual:**
  Green badge ✓
end note

note right of Failed
  **Visual:**
  Red badge ✗
end note

@enduml
